外国人创始人米克·琼斯透露，他“多年来”一直在与帕金森病作斗争https://www.nme.com/news/music/foreigner-Founder-mick-jones-reveals-he-has-been-batdling-parkinsons-disease-for-several-years-3591472?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=外国人创始人米克·琼斯透露，他多年来一直在与帕金森病作斗争Liberty DunworthThu, 22 Feb 2024 16:02:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3591472 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他发表声明称，应对这些症状是“每天的斗争”</p><p> 《<a href="https://www.nme.com">外国人</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foreigner-founder-mick-jones-reveals-he-has-been-battling-parkinsons-disease-for-several-years-3591472">》杂志创始人米克·琼斯 (Mick Jones) 透露，他“多年来”一直在与帕金森病作斗争</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mick-Jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foreigner">外国人</a>创始人米克·琼斯透露，他患有帕金森病，并已与此病斗争了“数年”。</p><p>这位79岁的音乐家是这支摇滚乐队仅存的最后一位原始成员，由于健康问题，自2022年以来一直无法与他们一起现场表演。这在一定程度上归因于神经退行性疾病，包括震颤、僵硬、平衡问题和行动缓慢等症状。</p><p>现在，这位音乐家与歌迷分享了一份声明，确认他患有帕金森病多年。</p><p> “粉丝们会非常清楚，我已经有一段时间没有和乐队一起在舞台上表演了。几年前，我被诊断出患有帕金森病。我希望每个人都知道我做得很好，”他在社交媒体上写道。</p><p> “然而，我一直喜欢在舞台上表现出最好的状态，但遗憾的是，目前我发现这有点困难。我仍然在《外国人》的幕后工作中发挥着重要作用，并且仍然存在，”他补充道。 “帕金森病是一种日常斗争；重要的是要坚持下去，并提醒自己我在音乐领域的辉煌职业生涯。我感谢所有多年来支持外国人并继续参加我们音乐会的歌迷——我想让你们知道，我感谢你们的支持；它对我来说总是意义重大，尤其是在我生命中的这个阶段。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3nLVltLXbd/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,3