-day-coverups-covers-nirvana-bowie-damned-guns-n-roses-video-setlist-2425880">他们邀请了Guns N&#39; Roses贝斯手Duff McKagan与他们一起演出</a>。</p><p> Green Day 上个月发行了第 14 张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737">《Saviors》</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-2024-saviors-stadium-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3529041">他们将于五月开始一场盛大的世界巡演</a>，英国和爱尔兰的巡演包括六月在温布利体育场的演出。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-pet-shop-boys-and-the-prodigy-to-headline-isle-of-wight-festival-2024-lineup-buy-tickets-3528939#:~:text=Prodigy%20to%20headline-,Green%20Day%2C%20Pet%20Shop%20Boys%20and%20The%20Prodigy%20to,Isle%20Of%20Wight%20Festival%202024&amp;text=Isle%20Of%20Wight%20Festival%20has,Newport%20between%20June%2020%2D23.">该三人组还将在今年的怀特岛音乐节上亮相</a>。</p><p>阿姆斯特朗等人宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-confirm-theyll-be-playing-dookie-and-american-idiot-in-full-on-2024-saviors-world-tour-3572429">他们将在“Saviors”巡演中完整演奏“American Idiot”和“Dookie”，</a>以分别纪念经典专辑的 20 周年和 30 周年。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/green-day-tickets/artist/768353?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xWpzsXyDbxyPRnUx98SctTxgUkFQv%3ATlnUsmUU0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找英国/爱尔兰日期的所有剩余门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-side-project-the-coverups-announce-intimate-london-show-buy-tickets-3591433">绿日乐队 (Green Day) 的副刊 The Coverups 宣布，亲密的伦敦演出</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
西伯利亚交响乐团键盘手维塔利·库普里 (Vitalij Kuprij) 去世，享年 49 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/trans-siberian-orchestra-keyboardist-vitalij-kuprij-dies-ged-49-3591442?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=trans-siberian-orchestra-keyboardist-vitalij-库普里吉 (kuprij) 去世，享年 49 岁Liberty DunworthThu, 22 Feb 2024 14:53:53 +0000 Music NewsNews..MetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3591442 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2014 年 1 月 11 日，美国前卫摇滚乐队西伯利亚交响乐团的键盘手维塔利·库普里 (Vitalij Kuprij) 在伦敦哈默史密斯阿波罗剧院的舞台上进行现场表演。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他参加了交响重金属乐队的 17 场巡演</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trans-siberian-orchestra-keyboardist-vitalij-kuprij-dies-aged-49-3591442">西伯利亚交响乐团键盘手 Vitalij Kuprij 去世，享年 49 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2014 年 1 月 11 日，美国前卫摇滚乐队西伯利亚交响乐团的键盘手维塔利·库普里 (Vitalij Kuprij) 在伦敦哈默史密斯阿波罗剧院的舞台上进行现场表演。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Vitalij-Kuprij@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>因与西伯利亚交响乐团合作而闻名的键盘手维塔利·库普里吉 (Vitalij Kuprij) 去世。他当时 49 岁。</p><p>他的死讯是由他的老朋友兼音乐合作伙伴、来自芬兰的吉他手兼制作人拉尔斯·埃里克·马特森 (Lars Eric Mattsson) 分享的。</p><p>据最新消息，这位著名的乌克兰裔美国键盘手于周二（2月20日）去世，享年49岁。死因尚未公布。</p><p> “今天早上醒来，我听到了非常悲伤的消息，我亲爱的朋友和键盘大师维塔利·库普里吉昨晚去世了，”马特森说。 “这位乌克兰出生的演奏家住在费城，最近与西伯利亚交响乐团一起进行了另一场非常成功的巡演。”</p><p> “我认识 Vitalij 并与 Vitalij 合作了 20 多年，他总是说要在芬兰见我去钓鱼，这是他继音乐之后的第二个爱好，”他补充道，“我们已经一起录制过几次，第一次是为了20 年前推出首张专辑《Book of Reflections》，后来又推出我的 MATTSSON 概念专辑《War》……。我的朋友，我会深深地想念你的！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3maMnttZXN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xli